1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,840
Cuatro.

2
00:00:00,840 --> 00:00:01,520
He encontrado

3
00:00:01,520 --> 00:00:02,520
cuatro cosas...

4
00:00:02,520 --> 00:00:03,360
en plena semana

5
00:00:03,360 --> 00:00:04,160
de Fallas.

6
00:00:04,160 --> 00:00:04,640
Y mirad

7
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:05,080
en qué estado.

8
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:05,760
Petardos,

9
00:00:05,760 --> 00:00:06,360
ninots,

10
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:07,040
fiesta por

11
00:00:07,040 --> 00:00:08,120
todas partes...

12
00:00:08,120 --> 00:00:09,400
y entre medio,

13
00:00:09,400 --> 00:00:10,240
cosas increíbles

14
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,520
tiradas en la acera.

15
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:12,320
Es que en Fallas

16
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:13,200
la gente limpia,

17
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:13,400
renueva,

18
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:14,480
cambia muebles...

19
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:14,960
y lo que no va

20
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:15,880
a durar aquí.

21
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:16,480
Mañana puede

22
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:17,320
que ya no esté.

23
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,320
O en el contenedor.

24
00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:19,280
Mirad lo que hago.

25
00:00:19,280 --> 00:00:19,680
Lo veo,

26
00:00:19,680 --> 00:00:20,480
lo subo a Givore,

27
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:20,920
y en nada

28
00:00:20,920 --> 00:00:21,600
alguien del barrio

29
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:22,400
lo descubre.

30
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:23,200
Mientras la ciudad

31
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:23,600
celebra,

32
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,520
vecinos conectando

33
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:25,240
sin conocerse.

34
00:00:25,240 --> 00:00:25,720
Segunda vida

35
00:00:25,720 --> 00:00:26,160
para todo.

36
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:26,720
Así que ojo

37
00:00:26,720 --> 00:00:27,440
esta semana.

38
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:27,840
Las calles

39
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:28,440
de Valencia

40
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:28,920
durante Fallas

41
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,000
son una mina.

42
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:30,480
Yo siempre

43
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:31,400
la llevo instalada.

44
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:32,440
Por si veis algo

45
00:00:32,440 --> 00:00:33,280
en la calle...

46
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:34,080
ya sabéis.

